nodes.text: The L05 adminmech was a model of adminmech droid. One L05 adminmech droid, C00-L05C, was forced to work in the spice mines of Kessel for the Pyke Syndicate. C00-L05C, along with the other droids in the Kessel control room, were freed from their restraining bolts after L3-37 started a slave uprising in the mines.
